Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface ScalarPropertyRangeRestrictionAxiom

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotatedElement, Axiom, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, PropertyRestrictionAxiom, RestrictionAxiom, ScalarPropertyRestrictionAxiom
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ScalarPropertyRangeRestrictionAxiomImpl
    public interface ScalarPropertyRangeRestrictionAxiom
extends ScalarPropertyRestrictionAxiom
    A representation of the model object 'Scalar Property Range Restriction Axiom'. ScalarPropertyRangeRestrictionAxiom is a scalar property restriction axiom that restricts the range of a property to a scalar that specializes the original range. This restrictions may apply to all or to some values of the property that have the restricting classifier as a domain.

    The following features are supported:

    • Range
    • Kind
